    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable companion that\u2019s ready to keep on rolling? This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and has plenty of life left for its next owner! It shows some character from its time on the road, with some visible wear that reflects its journey, but it remains a solid choice for anyone seeking dependable transportation at a great value. Get ready to enjoy the drive!",
